Description: Set segment length when interpolation.
Usage: M361 [P<units>]
Parameters:
[P<units>] Segment length when linear interpolation.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

-M362 – Set mm per arc segment

Description: Set segment length when interpolation.
Usage: M361 [P<units>]
Parameters:
[P<units>] segment length when arc interpolation.


